data.description: Embrace the serenity of nature with this 10-acre wooded wonderland! Nestled amidst a captivating mix of hardwoods, evergreens, fruit trees, and a lush berry patch, it's a haven for outdoor enthusiasts and wildlife lovers alike. Perfect for building your dream home or hunting cabin, with electric and natural gas ready at the road. Conveniently located close to Kalkaska, Mancelona and Traverse City. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make your Northern Michigan dreams a reality!
